{"calories":"950","carbs":103,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eWe love a brilliant pizza mashup, especially one inspired by our favorite restaurant dishes. In this recipe, Chef Michelle tranforms one of her favorite Paris bistro dishes, an arugula salad topped with sliced pears and crumbled blue cheese, into a dreamy pizza with caramelized onions and mozzarella. Some balsamic-dressed pears roast atop the pizza until tender and concentrated; the rest are tossed with arugula for a crisp salad that’s piled on top of the finished pie. This is the France-meets-Italy combo we never knew we always wanted.\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","difficulty":"medium","external_id":"d0f5f0d798","fat":47,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40848/KSlBo0iJRsKDlq5QZUdy_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0038___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40849/u8GFTaQQLiZJeMfz63wR_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0055___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40849/menu_small_u8GFTaQQLiZJeMfz63wR_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0055___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40847/2utaA08aRaKrr65JcF7j_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0050___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40847/hero_2utaA08aRaKrr65JcF7j_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0050___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40847/menu_small_2utaA08aRaKrr65JcF7j_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0050___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40847/small_square_2utaA08aRaKrr65JcF7j_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0050___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40847/medium_square_2utaA08aRaKrr65JcF7j_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0050___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40847/recipe_profile_page_2utaA08aRaKrr65JcF7j_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0050___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40850/large_cropped_AUC2TSCdSEGV1JzBHMkA_Blue_Cheese_Caramelized_Onion_Pizza_with_Pear_and_Arugula___0050___MAIN.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Blue Cheese–Caramelized Onion Pizza with Pear and Arugula","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"35-45","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":32,"public_slug":"blue-cheese-and-caramelized-onion-pizza-with-pear-balsamic-salad","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/24730/recipe_card20180216-9-lzg4s0.pdf","recipe_id":4095,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Blue Cheese–Caramelized Onion Pizza","subtitle":"with Pear and Arugula","title":"Blue Cheese–Caramelized Onion Pizza","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdding a little water to the onions helps keep them from burning in the pan. It also picks up the delicious browned bits that stick to the bottom, so your onions will be tastier and the pan will be easier to clean.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you don't have a rolling pin, try lifting the dough with your hands, letting gravity help stretch it down. Using your fingers, gently pull the edges, feeling for thicker areas so dough doesn’t tear.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["10\" medium high-sided pan","rolling pin (optional)","baking sheet"],"id":4095,"ingredients":["pizza dough","d'Anjou pear","Vidalia onion","unsalted butter","rosemary","flour","balsamic vinegar","shredded mozzarella and provolone cheese blend","blue cheese","baby arugula","parchment paper"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"pizza dough","quantity":"12.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1609/medium_square_medium_square_medium_square_pizza-dough.jpg"},{"name":"d'Anjou pear","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1116/medium_square_pear_danjou.jpg"},{"name":"Vidalia onion","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/896/medium_square_medium_square_ingredient-11.jpg"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/265/medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"rosemary","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1287/medium_square_medium_square_rosemary-fresh.jpg"},{"name":"flour","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/285/medium_square_FLOUR_copy.jpg"},{"name":"balsamic vinegar","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/3/medium_square_BALSAMIC_VINEGAR0019.jpg"},{"name":"shredded mozzarella and provolone cheese blend","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2305/medium_square_2017-02-09___DS_17130281.jpg"},{"name":"blue cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2187/medium_square_bleucheese.jpg"},{"name":"baby arugula","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/239/medium_square_arugula-test.jpg"},{"name":"parchment paper","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/203/medium_square_paper-parchment.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":15,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40851/recipe_card_size_58YZSLwxTHy4Zew6Tb2A_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Remove \u003cstrong\u003epizza dough\u003c/strong\u003e from bag and let soften at room temperature so it will be easier to roll out (we recommend about 15 minutes, so when the onions are cooked, you should be good to go). Rinse \u003cstrong\u003epear \u003c/strong\u003eand slice off rounded sides, discarding core, and cut lengthwise into .25-inch slices. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e, halve, and thinly slice.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Caramelize onion","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40854/recipe_card_size_n7ELUcOS1i0rhAFzfrxQ_2._Caramelize_Onions.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e in a medium high-sided pan over medium-high heat. When butter is foamy, add \u003cstrong\u003erosemary\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e, and\u003cstrong\u003e .25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and cook, stirring frequently, until light brown and softened, about 5 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003e.25 cup water \u003c/strong\u003eand reduce heat to medium. Cook, stirring continuously, until onion is golden and water has evaporated, 3-5 minutes more (see recipe tip). Remove and discard \u003cstrong\u003erosemary\u003c/strong\u003e. Set pan aside until Step 5.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roll out dough","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40852/recipe_card_size_ejFU6OSuQJKmg787YtMd_3._Roll_Out_Dough.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile onions cook, sprinkle \u003cstrong\u003eflour\u003c/strong\u003e onto a clean, dry surface, coating a rolling pin or your hands with a thin layer. Roll or stretch\u003cstrong\u003e pizza dough\u003c/strong\u003e into a rectangular shape, rotating frequently and working from center to edges, until .25-inch thick (see recipe tip). \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Bake pizza crust","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40853/recipe_card_size_TZnTr4aQMuogZYfwSlXA_4._Bake_Pizza_Crust_2X_3X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eLine a baking sheet with \u003cstrong\u003eparchment paper\u003c/strong\u003e and rub with \u003cstrong\u003e1 teaspoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e. Add\u003cstrong\u003e pizza dough\u003c/strong\u003e, gently stretching to reach edges of baking sheet, and rub all over with \u003cstrong\u003e2 teaspoons olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e. Season with \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e. Bake until crisp and lightly browned, 10-12 minutes. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Assemble pizza and bake","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40855/recipe_card_size_7tGH7siWQcOdgZYndRvq_5._Finish_Pizza_2X_3X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile crust bakes, in a large bowl, whisk together \u003cstrong\u003ebalsamic vinegar\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 cup olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Add \u003cstrong\u003epears\u003c/strong\u003e and toss to coat. Once crust is crisp, scatter over \u003cstrong\u003emozzarella and provolone\u003c/strong\u003e, then \u003cstrong\u003ecaramelized onion\u003c/strong\u003e, then \u003cstrong\u003eblue cheese\u003c/strong\u003e. Arrange \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of pears \u003c/strong\u003eover pizza in an even layer. Return to oven and bake until crust is browned and cheese is bubbling, 9-11 minutes. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate pizza and salad","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/40856/recipe_card_size_ozpoqvFvTCaVR9QFUDBx_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile pizza bakes, rinse \u003cstrong\u003earugula\u003c/strong\u003e and pat dry, then add to bowl with remaining pears and toss to combine. Once \u003cstrong\u003eblue cheese–caramelized onion pizza \u003c/strong\u003eis done, top with \u003cstrong\u003earugula and pear salad\u003c/strong\u003e and cut into slices, or serve the salad alongside. Dig in!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Soy","slug":"soy","hex_color":""},{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Bread","slug":"bread","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}